<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="110">7.2. Adding the Klarna Checkout category</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Create a second category of the type <strong>Container</strong>, so that the Klarna Checkout is displayed to the customer after selecting a country of delivery.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a category of the type container:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Categories</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>New category</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Create new category</strong> window will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
